# CubeMX-generated NUCLEO-H753ZI CMake project.
#
# We track the source of truth (tinychaos.ioc) plus everything we hand-edit
# (Core/, CMakeLists.txt, cmake/, startup, linker script). We do NOT track:
#
#   - build/   : CMake/Ninja output, always regenerable
#   - Drivers/ : ~1600 vendor HAL + CMSIS files, regenerated by CubeMX from
#                the .ioc (run the headless generate, see ../NUCLEO_SETUP.md).
#                Keeping them out of git keeps the diff readable.
#   - .mxproject / *.bak : CubeMX scratch + backups
#
# To rebuild Drivers/ on a fresh checkout: open tinychaos.ioc in CubeMX and
# Generate Code (or run the documented headless generate).

/build/
/Drivers/
.mxproject
*.bak
